The paper deals with coding schemes for wireless networks, which are typically studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the optimization of rate regions, which falls under the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. The simulations and implementation aspects of the proposed schemes may fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) sub-categories.
